Package tudarmstadt.lt.ABSentiment.featureExtractor

Feature extractors

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FeatureExtractor
    Interface for feature extractors.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AggregatedGazeteerFeature
    AggregatedGazeteerFeature class helps to extract aggregated lexicon feature based on the number of token occurrences in the input lexicon file Created by abhishek on 20/6/17.
    DocumentLengthFeature
    Document length FeatureExtractor, extracts normalized document length based on the precomputed maximal length.
    GazeteerFeature
    Gazeteer FeatureExtractor, extracts binary features if words from a word list are found in a document.
    PolarityLexiconFeature
    PolarityLexiconFeature class helps to extract polarity lexicon feature based on the polarity score of each token Created by abhishek on 11/7/17.
    TfIdfFeature
    TF-IDF FeatureExtractor, extracts normalized TF-IDF scores using a pre-computed IDF file.
    WordEmbeddingFeature
    Word Embedding FeatureExtractor, extracts the averaged word representation for an instance using a word embedding file.
